::Hevngjerrig::
       Aerotaur's programming worked quickly.  The CR tank went about it's 
regenerative process and altered his physical appearance at the same time.  
His silvery wings take on a dull black hue.  His body changes from metallic 
blues and reds to deep black with dull red highlights.  With his 
modifications complete he climbs out of the tank and stretches his newly 
painted joints.

--part1_115.2292fa62.2be09349_boundary
